Everyone who's been walking into the Cybertronian Fire lately (Battera and 
Wulvoritron), you can't just waltz in. The autoguns, laser batteries, missile 
launchers, and EMP cannons, not to mention the shields, would turn any 
unrecognized bot to slag in a few seconds. Please don't post for just walking 
in, let the defences or bots reply.

::Rex/Firearm::

Rex jumps back from the grenade, the explosion burning his leg. He growls, 
seeing Predator passes out, he turns and fires a missile at Imprisoner.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm ducks under five of Choran's shots, a few hitting him in the 
shoulder. The blast fired by Imprisoner passes a few feet over his shoulder.

The Maximal growls, setting his arm cannon on charge launcher and launching a 
charge at Choran.
